the author of three books on Meteorology,

1176
01:00:54,126 --> 01:00:59,104
...and an author and reviewer
on the UN's IPCC.

1177
01:01:00,599 --> 01:01:02,093
But when he conducted research

1178
01:01:02,094 --> 01:01:04,584
which was part funded
by the coal industry,

1179
01:01:04,585 --> 01:01:05,579
he found himself among those

1180
01:01:05,580 --> 01:01:08,567
under attack from
