right here, in London

1184
01:01:21,517 --> 01:01:23,508
and we have the right and the duty

1185
01:01:23,509 --> 01:01:25,500
to take it back into public ownership,
dismantle it, break it up

1186
01:01:25,501 --> 01:01:29,485
