01:01:30,980 --> 01:01:32,473
But reasoned debate...

1189
01:01:32,474 --> 01:01:35,460
is not the only casualty in
the global warming alarm.

1190
01:01:35,461 --> 01:01:38,449
As international public
policy bears down

1191
01:01:38,450 --> 01:01:40,442
on industrial emissions of CO2,

1192
01:01:40,443 --> 01:01:42,434
the developing world is coming

1193
01:01:42,435 --> 01:01:44,426
under intense pressure
not to develop.

